PROJECT STATUS : SUCCESSFULLY COMPLETED

CONCLUSION

This project successfully demonstrated Linux Administration and Docker Container Management in a multi-user environment. Different users were assigned responsibilities such as image creation, container deployment, monitoring, operations, volume creation, volume mapping, and persistence verification. Docker volume abcbank ensured that application data remained available even after container deletion, demonstrating the concept of persistent storage in Docker....
